titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on Trimethyl Base.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S5539)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/5/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1997, the duty on 1,3,3-trimethyl-2-methyleneindoline (trimethyl base).
